options.markdown:
Network Switch Metrics


Key system-level metrics for the host(s) that power this service

chart.description: Delta of bytes written/read to disk
chart.name: Disk I/O
chart.programText:
A = data('instance/disk/write_bytes_count', rollup='latest').sum().publish(label='A')
B = data('instance/disk/read_bytes_count', rollup='latest').sum().publish(label='B')

chart.name: Switch Availability
chart.programText:
A = data('cpu.utilization', filter=(not filter('agent', '*'))).mean(by=['host']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).max().publish(label='B')
C = (A).min().publish(label='C')
D = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='D')
E = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='E')
F = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='F')

options.markdown:
Compute Metrics


Key system-level metrics for the host(s) that power this service

chart.name: Output drops due to microburst
chart.programText:
A = data('if_errors.rx', rollup='rate').sum().publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('if_errors.tx', rollup='rate').sum().publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A+B).publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = (C).count().below(0, inclusive=True).publish(label='D', enable=False)
H = data('if_errors.rx', filter=filter('host_kernel_name', 'windows'), rollup='rate').sum().publish(label='H', enable=False)
I = data('if_errors.tx', filter=filter('host_kernel_name', 'windows'), rollup='rate').sum().publish(label='I', enable=False)
J = (H+I).publish(label='J', enable=False)
K = (J).count().below(0, inclusive=True).publish(label='K', enable=False)
L = (J*(D+1)).sum().publish(label='L')
M = (C*(K+1)).sum().publish(label='M')
N = (C+J).sum().publish(label='N')

chart.name: HTTP Response Count by Code
chart.programText:
D = data('http/server/response_count', filter=filter('response_code', '5*') and filter('module_id', 'default') and filter('project_id', 'molten-enigma-184614') and filter('version_id', 'sf-flex-engine')).sum(by=['project_id']).publish(label='D')
B = data('http/server/response_count', filter=filter('response_code', '3*') and filter('module_id', 'default') and filter('project_id', 'molten-enigma-184614') and filter('version_id', 'sf-flex-engine')).sum(by=['project_id']).publish(label='B')
C = data('http/server/response_count', filter=filter('response_code', '4*') and filter('module_id', 'default') and filter('project_id', 'molten-enigma-184614') and filter('version_id', 'sf-flex-engine'),rollup='rate').sum(by=['project_id']).publish(label='C')
A = data('http/server/response_count', filter=filter('response_code', '2*') and filter('module_id', 'default') and filter('project_id', 'molten-enigma-184614') and filter('version_id', 'sf-flex-engine'),rollup='rate').sum(by=['project_id']).publish(label='A')
